Africa News 24-7 has launched a new video series, where journalist Ayanda Mdluli will host a series of personalities to discuss pertinent issues in South Africa. Africa News 24-7 TV gives you an opportunity to listen to, and watch, as key industry players and analysts unpack the obstacles and possibilities around radical socioeconomic transformation in South Africa. In our first installment, Adil Nchabeleng, the president of Transform RSA joined Africa News24-7 journalist Ayanda in Sandton last week to talk about the state of the South African economy. According to Nchabeleng, SA’s economy is in a crisis and has been thrown into a tailspin as a result if ineffective leadership in SA’s power utility Eskom. Watch now: 